  <num>32-1231.09</num>
  <heading>Enforcement by civil action.</heading>
  <para>
    <num>(a)</num>
    <text>A civil action may be maintained against any employer in a court of competent jurisdiction by one or more employees.</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(b)</num>
    <text>An employer who violates the provisions of this chapter shall be liable to the affected employee or employees for the remedies set forth in <cite path="ยง32-1231.07|(c)">ยง 32-1231.07(c)</cite>.</text>
  </para>
